0place%20to%20find%20the%20talent%20to%20take%20you%20to%20the%20next%20level%20is%20obvious%3A%20the%20three%20biggest%20firms%20in%20the%20sector%2C%20Englander's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennium-org-chart-top-executives-izzy-englander-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMillennium%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Ken%20Griffin's%20Citadel%2C%20and%20Steve%20Cohen's%20Point72.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20firms%2C%20which%20manage%20more%20than%20%24180%20billion%20combined%20and%20employ%20more%20than%2010%2C000%20people%2C%20have%20become%20the%20recruiting%20grounds%20for%20firms%20in%20need%20of%20experienced%20executives%20in%20the%20same%20way%20that%20Julian%20Robertson's%20Tiger%20Management%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-tree-shows-how-many-tiger-cub-hedge-funds-there-are-2019-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewas%20once%20the%20launching%20pad%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20aspiring%20fund%20founders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20another%20example%20of%20the%20institutional%20qualities%20of%20the%20top%20tier%20of%20the%20%244.5%20trillion%20industry.%20Decades%20ago%20%E2%80%94%20when%20a%20hedge%20fund%20would%20have%20felt%20crowded%20with%20more%20than%20100%20people%20on%20staff%20%E2%80%94%20banks%2C%20consulting%20firms%2C%20law%20firms%2C%20and%20accounting%20giants%20served%20as%20feeders%20for%20hedge%20funds%20looking%20to%20fill%20out%20their%20executive%20ranks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20one%20could%20say%20they%20knew%20what%20it%20takes%20to%20run%20a%20multistrategy%20firm%20with%20tens%20of%20billions%20in%20capital%20because%20it%20had%20never%20been%20done.%20Now%20that's%20changed%2C%20and%20those%20involved%20with%20the%20day-to-day%20management%20of%20the%20biggest%20firms%20in%20the%20industry%20have%20become%20hot%20commodities%20for%20those%20hoping%20to%20break%20into%20the%20top%20tier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20sit%20in%20those%20circles%2C%20when%20you%20sit%20