f810b8c6ad288d147dd4b1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221857%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20tariffs%2C%20which%20start%20at%20a%20baseline%20rate%20of%2010%25%20and%20affect%20185%20countries%2C%20took%20effect%20on%20April%209.%3Cp%3EChip%20Somodevilla%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f02829e7-b7e3-431a-a9e8-df32bc1cceff%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20volatility%20is%20such%20a%20deal%20killer%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBankers%2C%20who%20requested%20anonymity%20because%20they%20weren't%20authorized%20to%20speak%20with%20the%20press%2C%20said%20they're%20watching%20one%20major%20metric%20as%20they%20advise%20companies%20on%20their%20next%20steps%20toward%20the%20public%20markets%3A%20the%20volatility%20index.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20index%2C%20which%20has%20the%20ticker%20VIX%2C%20is%20designed%20to%20measure%20the%2030-day%20expected%20volatility%20of%20the%20stock%20market.%20VIX%20values%20of%2030%20or%20above%20generally%20signal%20high%20volatility%2C%20while%20values%20of%2020%20or%20below%20signal%20more%20stability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMarket%20volatility%20doesn't%20necessarily%20correlate%20with%20lower%20all-time%20public%20market%20valuations.%20But%20high%20volatility%20makes%20it%20much%20harder%20for%20public%20investors%20to%20price%20a%20potential%20IPO%2C%20like%20trying%20to%20hit%20a%20moving%20target%2C%20bankers%20said.%20Plus%2C%20the%20volatility%20makes%20those%20investors%20less%20confident%20that%20the%20company's%20stock%20won't%20tank%20after%20the%20IPO%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMatt%20Kennedy%2C%20a%20senior%20strategist%20at%20Renaissance%20Capital%2C%20said%20the%20index%20would%20need%20to%20settle%20below%2025%20for%20several%20consecutive%20weeks%20for%20IPO%20activity%20to%20meaningfully%20pick%20up.%20Other%20sources%20told%20BI%20they'd%20want%20the%20index%20to%20stay%20below%2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERight%20now%2C%20that%20target%20looks%20far%20away.%20At%20its%20peak%20Thursday%2C%20the%20index%20leaped%2052%25%20to%2054%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20volatility%20certainly%20isn't%20encouraging%20companies%20to%20start%20the%20roadshow%20now.%20Whether%20the%20stock%20market%20goes%20up%20or%20down%20over%20the%20next%20couple%20of%20weeks%2C%20there%20will%20be%20very%20few%20quality%20companies%20going%20public%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jay%20Ritter%2C%20a%20finance%20professor%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Florida.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225269%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Stock%20market%20numbers%20at%20the%20NYSE%20during%20morning%20trading%20on%20April%2010%2C%202025.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f80eefa466d2b74ab2d686%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223952%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20volatility%20index%20surged%20Thursday%20on%20Trump's%20trade%20war%20with%20China.%3Cp%3EMichael%20M.%20Santiago%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22285f446a-31ce-4b25-b986-d4f0c59bd32e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EEven%20if%20the%20market%20stabilizes%2C%20expect%20discounts%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20market%20ticks%20back%20up%20and%20volatility%20remains%20low%20for%20multiple%20consecutive%20weeks%2C%20some%20public%20investors%20may%20be%20willing%20to%20put%20funds%20toward%20IPOs%20again.%20But%20they'll%20expect%20a%20significant%20price%20cut%2C%20Kennedy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAny%20sensible%20investor%20would%20still%20demand%20a%20pretty%20substantial%20discount%20to%20buy%20IPOs%20in%20this%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAfter%20all%2C%20if%20we%20get%20more%20turbulence%2C%20IPOs%20will%20be%20the%20first%20to%20sell%20off.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBankers%20said%20that%20if%20companies%20are%20willing%20to%20accept%20that%20discount%2C%20they%20may%20still%20be%20able%20to%20go%20public%20in%20the%20second%20quarter%20of%20this%20year%2C%20provided%20that%20t