ssible%2C%20he%20urged%20the%20Congress%20to%20project%20itself%20as%20a%20party%20of%20hope%20and%20positivity%2C%20not%20resentment%20and%20criticism%2C%20and%20as%20a%20party%20of%20the%20future%2C%20not%20just%20of%20the%20past.%20The%20youth%2C%20he%20reminded%20those%20present%2C%20do%20not%20give%20much%20importance%20to%20history%20but%20look%20for%20ideas%20for%20their%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETharoor's%20words%20assume%20significance%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20present%20Congress%20leadership's%20tendency%20to%20hark%20back%20to%20its%20glorious%20past%20by%20repeatedly%20recalling%20its%20pivotal%20role%20in%20the%20freedom%20struggle%20and%20the%20sacrifices%20of%20its%20slain%20leaders%20Indira%20and%20Rajiv%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20propensity%20to%20live%20in%20the%20past%20oozed%20out%20of%20every%20pore%20during%20the%20two-day%20session.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20entire%20meet%20was%20high%20on%20historical%20symbolism%20with%20pointed%20markers%20of%20the%20party's%20rich%20legacy%3A%20a%20Congress%20Working%20Committee%20meet%20at%20the%20Sardar%20Vallabhbhai%20Patel%20Memorial%20in%20Ahmedabad%2C%20a%20visit%20to%20Mahatma%20Gandhi's%20Sabarmati%20Ashram%2C%20a%20break%20from%20tradition%20in%20favour%20of%20one%20omnibus%20resolution%20adopted%20in%20honour%20of%20India's%20%E2%80%98Iron%20Man'%2C%20Sardar%20Vallabhbhai%20Patel.%20Posters%20and%20banners%20of%20Gandhi%20and%20Patel%20studded%20the%20venues%20as%20the%20party%20made%20a%20desperate%20bid%20to%20reclaim%20these%20national%20icons%20from%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%2C%20which%20has%20glorified%20Patel%20in%20particular%20by%20consecrating%20the%20world's%20tallest%20statue%20in%20his%20image.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Well-Planned%20Conspiracy'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20drove%20home%20the%20point%20further%2C%20with%20a%20resolution%20condemning%20what%20it%20termed%20as%20%E2%80%9Ca%20well-planned%20conspiracy%E2%80%9D%20against%20national%20heroes.%20The%20resolution%20described%20the%20BJP's%20bid%20to%20claim%20Patel's%20legacy%20as%20%E2%80%9Claughable%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20appreciating%20the%20driving%20need%20to%20remind%20the%20country%20that%20it%20was%20the%20Congress%20that%20birthed%20the%20heroes%20of%20the%20freedom%20struggle%20who%20are%20being%20deified%20by%20the%20BJP%20today%2C%20it's%20time%20for%20the%20party%20to%20stop%20living%20off%20its%20past%20glories.%20This%20is%20the%2021st%20century.%20The%20freedom%20struggle%20was%20fought%20and%20won%20nearly%2080%20years%20ago.%20Most%20of%20the%20country's%20youth%20do%20not%20remember%20or%20do%20not%20care%20to%20remember%20that%20era.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20median%20age%20in%20India%20is%2028.5%20years.%20It's%20a%20young%20population%20driven%20by%20aspirations%20to%20get%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20the%20Congress%20of%20the%20past%20does%20not%20resonate%20with%20this%20demographic.%20Tharoor%20was%20not%20wrong%20when%20he%20said%20that%20the%20youth%20don't%20attach%20much%20importance%20to%20history.%20They%20look%20to%20the%20future%20and%20want%20to%20know%20how%20the%20Congress%20can%20help%20them%20get%20ahead%20and%20fulfill%20their%20dreams.%20The%20current%20crop%20of%20Congress%20strategists%20would%20do%20well%20to%20recall%20how%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20paraphrased%20the%20famous%20words%20of%20Martin%20Luther%20King%20Jr%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20too%20have%20a%20dream%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%20and%20reached%20out%20to%20a%20young%20population%20raring%20to%20storm%20into%20the%2021st%20century%20with%20computers%2C%20skill-based%20education%2C%20drinking%20water%20on%20tap%20and%20a%20corruption-free%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPlaying%20To%20Its%20Strengths%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20as%20a%20name%20has%20immense%20brand%20recall.%20After%20all%2C%20it%20has%20been%20around%20for%20almost%20140%20years.%20However%2C%20it%20needs%20to%20pour%20new%20wine%20into%20old%20bottles%20to%20strike%20a%20chord%20with%20the%20burgeoning%20population%20of%20young%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20fair%2C%20the%20AICC%20session%20did%20attempt%20incremental%20changes%20in%20messaging.%20For%20instance%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20it%20took%20the%20bull%20by%20the%20horns%20and%20challenged%20the%20BJP's%20view%20of%20nationalism.%20Dismissing%20it%20as%20%E2%80%9Cpseudo-nationalism%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20Congress%20made%20an%20effort%20to%20define%20its%20own%20brand%20of%20the%20concept%2C%20which%20it%20described%20as%20one%20that%20binds%20people%20together%20instead%20of%20dividing%20them%2C%20and%20one%20that%20is%20deeply%20embedded%20in%20our%20shared%20heritage%2C%20not%20in%20vitriol%20and%20prejudice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20concept%20is%20still%20evolving%20and%20needs%20refining%2C%20but%20at%20least%20the%20Congress%20has%20started%20the%20process.%3Cbr%3E%5CnOn%20secularism%2C%20too%2C%20the%20Congress%20is%20still%20trying%20to%20frame%20its%20position.%20However%2C%20it%20did%20try%20a%20bolder%20approach%20this%20time%20by%20specifically%20identifying%20Muslims%20and%20Christians%20as%20victims%20of%20violence%2C%20instead%20of%20waffling%20about%20%E2%80%9Creligious%20minorities%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EStay%20Positive%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20there%20is%20a%20section%20within%20the%20party%20that%20has%20reservations%20about%20the%20constant%20harping%20on%20caste%20and%20caste%20census.%20This%20is%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20new%20obsession%2C%20and%20while%20a%20census%20will%20certainly%20help%20the%20cause%20of%20equitable%20social%20justice%2C%20some%20wonder%20whether%20constant%20talk%20of%20historical%20atrocities%20on%20the%20marginalised%20injects%20negativity%20into%20the%20party's%20discourse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETharoor%20talked%20of%20the%20need%20for%20positivity.%20Perhaps%20the%20Congress%20should%20concentrate%20on%20crafting%20a%20well-defined%20agenda%20with%20a%20futuristic%20vision%20for%20the%20nation%2C%20something%20like%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20did%20back%20in%20the%20mid-1980s%2C%20instead%20of%20focusing%20all%20its%20energies%20on%20a%20negative%20campaign%20against%20the%20BJP%20and%20RSS.%20The%20Ahmedabad%20meet%20would%20have%20been%20a%20good%20place%20to%20start%20brainstorming%20on%20this.%20It%20would%20have%20certainly%C2%A0sent%20out%20a%20message%20of%20change.%20Unfortunately%2C%20the%20Congress%20failed%20to%20seize%20this%20opportunity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20author%20is%20a%20senior%20Delhi-based%20journalist)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20authors%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744352340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Fa65j489c_congrss_625x300_11_April_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhy-almost-nothing-at-all-happened-at-congress-historic-gujarat-meet-8138343%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20a%20senior%20leader%20who%20spoke%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20anonymity%20remarked%20in%20a%20despondent%20tone%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20seem%20to%20have%20moved%20forward%20from%20where%20we%20stood%20in%202020.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhy-almost-nothing-at-all-happened-at-congress-historic-gujarat-meet-8138343%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Emraan%20Hashmi%20recalls%20his%20son%E2%80%99s%20heartbreaking%20cancer%20battle%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744352041000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-120196609%2Cimgsize-1209250.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Femraan-hashmi-recalls-his-sons-heartbreaking-cancer-battle