ugust%20covering%20many%20aspects%20everyday%20life%20in%20Afghanistan%2C%20including%20public%20transport%2C%20music%2C%20shaving%20and%20celebrations.%20Most%20notably%2C%20the%20ministry%20issued%20a%20ban%20on%20women's%20voices%20and%20bare%20faces%20in%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20same%20month%2C%20a%20top%20U.N.%20official%20warned%20the%20laws%20provided%20a%20%26quot%3Bdistressing%20vision%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20country's%20future%20by%20adding%20to%20existing%20employment%2C%20education%2C%20and%20dress%20code%20restrictions%20on%20women%20and%20girls.%20Taliban%20officials%20have%20rejected%20U.N.%20concerns%20about%20the%20morality%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThursday's%20report%2C%20from%20the%20U.N.%20mission%20in%20Afghanistan%2C%20said%20in%20the%20first%206%20months%20of%20the%20laws'%20implementation%2C%20over%20half%20of%20detentions%20made%20under%20it%20concerned%20%26quot%3Beither%20men%20not%20having%20the%20compliant%20beard%20length%20or%20hairstyle%2C%20or%20barbers%20providing%20non-compliant%20beard%20trimming%20or%20haircuts.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20said%20that%20the%20morality%20police%20regularly%20detained%20people%20arbitrarily%20%26quot%3Bwithout%20due%20process%20and%20legal%20protections.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20holy%20fasting%20month%20of%20Ramadan%2C%20men's%20attendance%20at%20mandated%20congregational%20prayers%20was%20closely%20monitored%2C%20leading%20at%20times%20to%20arbitrary%20detention%20of%20those%20who%20didn't%20show%20up%2C%20the%20report%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20U.N.%20mission%20said%20that%20both%20sexes%20were%20negatively%20affected%2C%20particularly%20people%20with%20small%20businesses%20such%20as%20private%20education%20centers%2C%20barbers%20and%20hairdressers%2C%20tailors%2C%20wedding%20caterers%20and%20restaurants%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20reduction%20or%20total%20loss%20of%20income%20and%20employment%20opportunities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20direc