l%20Lake%2C%20I%20wondered%2C%20where%20do%20these%20go%20once%20they%20pile%20up.%20The%20lake%E2%80%99s%20beauty%20was%20being%20marred%20by%20this%20seemingly%20useless%20material.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%20raised%20in%20Meerut%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Maninder%E2%80%99s%20journey%20as%20a%20social%20entrepreneur%20took%20an%20unconventional%20turn%20from%20the%20very%20beginning.%20While%20pursuing%20his%20law%20degree%20at%20ILS%20Law%20College%20in%20Pune%2C%20he%20was%20on%20the%20lookout%20for%20opportunities%20to%20utilise%20his%20time%20better.%20In%202009%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20launch%20his%20own%20IT-based%20education%20company.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMr.-Maninder-Singh-Founder-CEO-CEF-Group-1_11zon-1744205472-500x643.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Maninder%20Singh%20was%20always%20passionate%20about%20creating%20a%20social%20enterprise%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMr.-Maninder-Singh-Founder-CEO-CEF-Group-1_11zon-1744205472-500x643.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMr.-Maninder-Singh-Founder-CEO-CEF-Group-1_11zon-1744205472-233x300.jpg%20233w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMr.-Maninder-Singh-Founder-CEO-CEF-Group-1_11zon-1744205472-768x988.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMr.-Maninder-Singh-Founder-CEO-CEF-Group-1_11zon-1744205472-1194x1536.jpg%201194w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMr.-Maninder-Singh-Founder-CEO-CEF-Group-1_11zon-1744205472-1593x2048.jpg%201593w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMr.-Maninder-Singh-Founder-CEO-CEF-Group-1_11zo