to%20Dal%20Lake%20in%202013%20that%20inspired%20his%20most%20impactful%20idea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20aquatic%20plants%20had%20accumulated%20near%20Dal%20Lake%20over%20the%20years%2C%20creating%20an%20unsightly%20mess%20and%20posing%20a%20threat%20to%20the%20local%20ecosystem%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20Previous%20efforts%20by%20the%20government%20and%20various%20organisations%20had%20failed%20to%20find%20an%20effective%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20brought%20some%20lake%20weed%20back%20to%20Delhi%20and%20tested%20it%20in%20labs%2C%20including%20PFT%20Gurugram%2C%20Shree%20Ram%20Testing%20Laboratory%20in%20Ghaziabad%2C%20and%20two%20labs%20in%20Sweden.%20I%20discovered%20that%20the%20weeds%20were%20rich%20in%20carbohydrates%20and%20could%20be%20used%20to%20create%20organic%20manure%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20insight%20led%20Maninder%20to%20establish%20%E2%80%98CEF%20Group%20(CleanEffentech)%E2%80%99%20in%202016%2C%20a%20company%20dedicated%20to%20addressing%20environmental%20degradation%2C%20soil%20erosion%2C%20and%20waste%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-02-26-at-12.15.57_fc70d7dc-1-1744205570.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22By%202018%2C%20Maninder%20proposed%20his%20solution%20to%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20government%2C%20to%20tackle%20the%20lake%20weed%20issue%20in%20Dal%20Lake%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%