1744205295-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-418900%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20re-introduction%20of%20native%20plant%20species%20is%20focused%20upon%20during%20the%20reforestation%20projects%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Aravalli%20range%20is%20one%20of%20the%20oldest%20fold%20mountains%20in%20India%20and%20plays%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20protecting%20the%20NCR%20region%20from%20desertification.%20The%20plant%20has%20degraded%20much%20of%20the%20Aravalli%20landscape%20and%20years%20of%20degradation%20have%20weakened%20its%20natural%20barriers%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jagdish%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20most%20viable%20antidote%20would%20be%20the%20integration%20of%20diverse%20native%20species%20like%20%3Cem%3Edhau%20%3C%2Fem%3E(%3Cem%3EAnogeissus%20pendula%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20%3Cem%3Edhak%20%3C%2Fem%3E(%3Cem%3EButea%20monosperma%3C%2Fem%3E)%20and%20%3Cem%3Esalai%20%3C%2Fem%3E(%3Cem%3EBoswellia%20serrata%3C%2Fem%3E)%20to%20restore%20the%20ecological%20balance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20CATCH%20Foundation%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20for%20reforestation%20in%20the%20NSG%20campus%20are%20a%20step%20towards%20this.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20blueprint%20for%20building%20a%20forest%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20forest%2C%20having%20trees%20of%20varying%20heights%20is%20good%20from%20two%20standpoints%20%E2%80%94%20they%20support%20different%20species%2C%20and%20they%20influence%20different%20levels%20of%20light%20and%20water%20availability.%20The%20CATCH%20Foundation%20model%20is%20cognisant%20of%20this.%20It%20accounts%20for%20plants%20of%20every%20height%2C%20from%20shrub%20layers%20(6%20feet)%20to%20the%20canopy%20layers%20(above%2040%20feet).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20s