0delicious%20harvest%20of%20vitamin-rich%20fruit.%20Growing%20passion%20fruit%20at%20home%20is%20easier%20than%20you%20think%2C%20and%20the%20following%20step-by-step%20guide%20will%20help%20you%20on%20your%20way%20to%20cultivating%20this%20tropical%20treat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E1.%20Let%20the%20sunshine%20in%3A%20Pick%20the%20ideal%20spot%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPassion%20fruit%20survives%20in%20sunny%20locations%2C%20so%20select%20a%20place%20that%20enjoys%20at%20least%206%20hours%20of%20sunlight%20each%20day.%20A%20south-facing%20wall%20or%20a%20sunny%20patio%20is%20perfect.%20If%20you%20live%20in%20cooler%20regions%2C%20consider%20planting%20passion%20fruit%20in%20a%20pot%20so%20you%20can%20bring%20it%20indoors%20during%20colder%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E2.%20Get%20the%20soil%20ready%20for%20a%20successful%20harvest%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPassion%20fruit%20loves%20well-drained%20and%20fertile%20soil.%20For%20the%20best%20results%2C%20aim%20for%20slightly%20acidic%20to%20neutral%20pH%20levels%20(6.5%20to%20seven).%20If%20your%20soil%20is%20heavy%20or%20clayey%2C%20enrich%20it%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F413829%2Fmana-shah-founder-green-practices-mumbai-turns-waste-compost-free-world-recycling-day%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecompost%20or%20organic%20matter%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20improve%20its%20drainage%20and%20nutrient%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F20